OCI of South Korea Says It Is Considering Selling GDRsto Fund Expansion

-- B y   S h i n h y e   K a n g
-- 
2011-03-30T06:25:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-30/oci-of-south-korea-says-it-is-considering-selling-gdrsto-fund-expansion.html
OCI Co. is considering various
measures including selling global depository receipts to raise
funds for expansion, according to a regulatory filing by the
South Korean polysilicon maker. The company is seeking to
raising $500 million by selling global depository receipts,
MoneyToday earlier reported, citing an unidentified industry
official.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
